description: A rare custom-renovated single-family home on coveted K Street, this large detached residence showcases exceptional detail throughout. Features include herringbone floors, custom millwork, a walk-in pantry, mudroom, and outdoor kitchen. The chef’s kitchen boasts inset cabinetry, Thermador appliances, and an 11-foot island. The primary suite offers a private sitting room/office, spa-like bath with trough sink, and a massive, custom walk-in closet designed to impress. A second bedroom, full bath, and laundry complete this level. The third floor offers two spacious bedrooms and another full bath. A walkout basement finished with heating, cooling, electrical, and drywall provides excellent in-law or au pair potential.
